basic_usage.description: Basic form filling with pattern matching

openai_usage.command: python3 agentic_form_filler.py --form form.pdf --sources data1.pdf data2.txt --ai-provider openai --api-key sk-... --output filled.pdf

anthropic_usage.command: python3 agentic_form_filler.py --form form.pdf --sources data.pdf --ai-provider anthropic --model claude-3-sonnet --api-key sk-ant-... --output filled.pdf

quality_assurance.command: python3 agentic_form_filler.py --form form.pdf --sources data.pdf --ai-provider anthropic --max-iterations 5 --output filled.pdf

framework_usage.command: python3 python_agentic_framework.py --form form.pdf --sources data1.txt data2.pdf --ai-provider openai --output filled.pdf
